//-       ## The Problem
//-       My bounce rate is high, and that is bad. People that are checking out my website are generally those looking to hire or collaborate and I want them to stick around long enough to get an idea of what I am really about. 
//-       
//-       ## A Little History
//-       I have owned andrewglassett.com for 5 years now, and in that time I have redesigned the site at least 10 times. My website has been on Wordpress, Squarespace, Ghost, Jekyll, and even my own markup and style. Wordpress can be slow, Squarespace a little rigid, and Ghost requires me to change my hosting. Using my own markup can be difficult to update the content and style.
